1] package.json is a configuration for npm.

2] there are two types of packages

one is dev depencies
in the development phase

and normal depency
production also

3] package-lock.json - keeps a track of exact version of package
package.json - keeps a track of version of the package but will have a caret or tilda which will give approx version.

4] node_modules - contains all the code we fetch from npm

